Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Browser fingerprinting detected

Solution: Use Tor browser for additional anonymity
Verify privacy.resistFingerprinting is enabled
Clear cookies between sessions
Issue: Email verification failing

Solution: Use different email provider (Tutanota, Guerrilla Mail)
Wait 24 hours before attempting verification
Check spam folder for verification emails
Issue: Account suspended immediately

Solution: IP address may be flagged; use VPN/Tor
Slow down account creation (1 per day maximum)
Ensure browser has proper OPSEC configuration
Build account history gradually
